  "elapsed_s": 13.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we came-- it took us a couple of weeks, we came to a place [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in a coal mine place.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The name is Sorokino, was the name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Sorokino.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they put us in a-- in a building before the [? shocks, ?] we calling it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And they put this in a room, and this room was seven beds.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Was beds already down there, seven beds.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Seven people was living in this particular-- each room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Was no running water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The bathrooms were outside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And they give us again money, and they took us to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] means the grocery store, the big store.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Now in Russia, it doesn't exist, if somebody wants to buy something in the store, he must be in the line a couple hours.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "It's not important what you want to buy, but because whenever you come, is a line. 50, 100, 200 people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Now with the privilege which we got because they bring us in here, that the-- the person which was going, it was a commissar.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And he opened up, and he let us in before.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "This for the privilege that we can-- we don't need to wait in line.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And we bought everything, and I tried already from this particular moment, I tried-- I bought different items which I don't need, and I sold it to these people who are staying in the line.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] All kind-- all kind tricks we did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "We did-- And then they took us to visit the coal mine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The visit, that means what kind of job we want to everybody can pick their own job.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
